I"f<p>The beauty consultation App is an IOS application for engaging in-store experience. When a customer enter the store, beauty artist(BA) will use this App to perform a skin consultant with customer and suggest products to her/ him.</p>

<p>The App includes</p>

<ul>
  <li>APIs integration to
    <ul>
      <li>search member</li>
      <li>get product information</li>
      <li>create new member</li>
      <li>send product recommandation and skin consult record to brandâ€™s CRM system</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>form to register member
    <ul>
      <li>e-Signature</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>product catalogue
    <ul>
      <li>product sorting</li>
      <li>video playing</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>push notification for database update</li>
  <li>language changing</li>
</ul>

